MCP的屏幕视觉分析工具，支持本地截图+Ollama/Dashscope双后端识别，实现UI理解与内容摘要。","descriptionEn":"这个项目是一个使用 FastMCP 框架实现的屏幕截图工具，它能够捕获屏幕内容，并通过 Ollama API 或者是阿里云的 Dashscope 发送给视觉模型进行分析。\n\n- **屏幕截图**：使用 `ImageGrab` 捕获整个屏幕，并调整图像大小\n  python\n  from PIL import ImageGrab\n  screenshot = ImageGrab.grab()\n  resized_image = screenshot.resize((800, 600))\n  \n\n- **Base64 编码**：将截图转换为 Base64 编码的 data URL\n  python\n  import base64\n  from io import BytesIO\n\n  buffered = BytesIO()\n  resized_image.save(buffered, format=\"PNG\")\n  img_str = base64.b64encode(buffered.getvalue()).decode(\"utf-8\")\n  data_url = f\"data:image/png;base64,{img_str}\"\n  \n\n- **Ollama API 调用**：将 Base64 编码的图像发送给 Ollama API\n  python\n  import requests\n\n  url = \"https://api.ollama.com/analyze\"\n  headers = {\n      \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n      \"Authorization\": \"Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\"\n  }\n  payload = {\n      \"image\": data_url\n  }\n\n  response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=payload)\n  print(response.json())","category":"development","tags":["屏幕识别","视觉分析","Ollama","Dashscope","UI理解","本地AI","开发调试","多模型适配"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"Alnesti-To_getscreen","securityScore":47,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/ALNESTI/mcp-server-get-the-screen","source":"modelscope","configHint":"Windows需额外安装Pillow依赖；推荐使用Dashscope作为默认后端","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["UI自动化测试","桌面操作理解","无障碍辅助","开发者视觉调试"]},{"serverId":"@SiddheshDongare-GIT-Pilot","friendlyName":"GitHub驾舱","friendlyNameEn":"GitHub飞行员","description":"FastMCP架构的GitHub统一API网关，提供标准化接口封装，覆盖仓库、PR、Issue、Actions等全部核心能力，内置OAuth2安全认证。","descriptionEn":"通过基于FastMCP的服务器为GitHub操作提供了一个全面的API包装器，简化了仓库管理、拉取请求、问题和其他GitHub交互，并具有安全的身份验证。","category":"development","tags":["API网关","GitHub封装","FastMCP","OAuth2","开发者平台","微服